Creating a Makefile:

Open the terminal to the project directory.
Type "./make.sh cutthepower"

The Makefile will be generated containing all of the correct files automatically.

Makefile commands:
make			= compiles the updated source files
make run		= compiles the updated source files and runs the game
make debug		= compiles the updated source files with GDB nd runs the game with GDB
make clean		= removes all of the object files and binary files.
